Gemini on terminal

ai [OPTIONS] promt


OPTIONS

	-i	--init			Create the config file for this aplication
	-o					Configure the default promt for the AI, changing the behaviour of the AI
	-t	--API_KEY		Configure the API-KEY
	-s	--save FILE		Toggle the history of chats
	-r	--read FILE		Show the history
	-T	--s2t0			Speech to text ui
	-C	--configure		Open the configuration file